issue.title: Minimal flatten
issue.body:
* features Minimal flatten option, to resolve $ref's only
* features Verbose and RemoveUnused options
* features OAIGen resolve, an attempt to resolve name conflicts with fewer extra definitions
* features JSON pointer resolver, to render a spec with only $ref to top level definitions
* more godoc
* more UT
* contributes go-swagger/go-swagger#1572

issue.title: Update vendor 20180630
issue.body:
This PR updates vendor dependencies.

It follows PR #1568 

It is essentially focused on testing go-openapi/analysis#30 (currently forced to a branch at my fork) 
and in particular, non-regression testing with the new flatten behavior (e.g. maps are simple types).

This testing uncovered some bugs, which are fixed in a distinct commit (now squashed).

Complementary integration work on go-swagger (CLI update, more testing with newly available options) will come as a separate PR.

Cheers,

Fred

issue.title: Fail to generate model: unhandled type to resolve JSON pointer
issue.body:
## Problem statement

We are using go-swagger v0.12 to generate types, which works fine. We hope to upgrade go-swagger to the latest version without incompatibility and benefit from other feature. I think #1572 help a lot. However, I fail to generate model with latest version of go-swagger.

run
```bash
swagger generate model -f swagger.yml
```

I got error
```
2018/07/05 14:09:30 validating spec /mnt/hgfs/vmshare/go/src/github.com/alibaba/pouch/hack/../apis/swagger.yml
2018/07/05 14:09:33 preprocessing spec with option:  minimal flattening
unhandled type to resolve JSON pointer: spec.Response
```

debug mode
```
...
analysis:2018/07/05 14:29:08 flatten.go:1401: normalizeRef
analysis:2018/07/05 14:29:08 flatten.go:1222: name pointers
analysis:2018/07/05 14:29:08 flatten.go:1336: deepestRef for #/responses/401ErrorResponse
unhandled type to resolve JSON pointer: spec.Response
```

## Swagger specification
https://github.com/alibaba/pouch/blob/master/apis/swagger.yml

## Environment
swagger version: build from master a6de9fc6ed034d2bc27c0818571f888ec59084eb
go version: 1.9.7  
OS:   ubuntu 18.04
